# SqlTxt.Storage

On-disk persistence with human-readable text formats.

## Directory Layout

```
/MyDatabase/
  db.manifest.json
  /system/
    tables.meta.txt
    engine.meta.json
  /tables/
    /Users/
      schema.txt
      data.txt
      table.meta.txt
```

## File Formats

- **schema.txt** — `TABLE:`, `FORMAT_VERSION:`, `COLUMNS:` with pipe-delimited column definitions
- **table.meta.txt** — `ROW_COUNT`, `ACTIVE_ROW_COUNT`, `DELETED_ROW_COUNT`, `LAST_UPDATED_UTC`
- **data.txt** — Fixed-width positional rows with soft-delete marker (A| or D|)

## Guidelines

- All formats must be human-readable and diff-friendly.
- Use `IFileSystemAccessor` to abstract file I/O for testability.
- Implement `ISchemaStore`, `ITableDataStore`, `IMetadataStore`.
- Support format versioning for future evolution.
